A simple linux app that show desktop notifications when keyboard lock keys are pressed.

On ubuntu requires: python, python-gtk, python-notify e python-xorg.

How to install:

git clone git://github.com/fenrrir/Pyledkeys.git
cd Pyledkeys
sudo python setup.py install

How to add to gnome session:

https://help.ubuntu.com/community/AddingProgramToSessionStartup




